dct_title_s: Salisburgensis iurisdictionis, locorumque vicinorum vera descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows hundreds and main roads. Date of publication from Koeman. Text in French in verso with caption title: Leicester-Shire; p. 241-242; signature Ffff. From: Le Theâtre du monde ou nouvel atlas / mis en lumière par Guillaume et Jean Blaeu. Amsterdami : Apud Iohannem Blaeu, 1645-1648.
